   <text>
      <body>
         <div>
            <pb facs="1862_02_21_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Bourjau_Hubener_Co_Shanghai_1.tif" n="1"/>
            <p>
               <seg rend="right">
                  <hi rend="latintype">
                     <placeName ref="K00503">Shanghai</placeName> d: <date when="1862-02-21">21<hi rend="superscript">ten</hi> Febr. 62</date>
                  </hi>
                  <lb/> Herren <hi rend="latintype">
                     <orgName type="firm" ref="K01004">L. Kniffler<lb/>&amp; C.</orgName>
                     <lb/>
                     <placeName ref="K00514">Nagasaki</placeName>
                  </hi>
               </seg> In Verfolg. <choice>
                  <abbr>u/.</abbr>
                  <expan> unseres</expan>
               </choice>
               <lb/> Schreibens mit dieser <lb/>Gelegenheit wollten <lb/>wir nicht unterlassen
                    <lb/>haben Ihnen noch <lb/>mit <add resp="writer" style="textOrientation: straight" place="above">zu</add> geben daß <del rend="overstrike">wir</del>
               <lb/> eine Frachtofferte <lb/> die wir dem <persName ref="K00114">Captain</persName>
               <lb/> des <unclear reason="eccentric_ductus" cert="medium">Hounds</unclear>
                    machten<lb/> nicht vorgenommen <lb/>wurde + daß der- <lb/>selbe jetzt in weni-
                    <lb/>gen Tagen nach <lb/>Ihrem Platze verse- <lb/>geln wird. wahrschein-
                    <lb/>lich suchend auf Spe- <lb/>kulation Wir bo- <lb/>ten ihm hier <measure type="commercial">$</measure>
               <measure type="currency" quantity="6" unit="mex$">6.</measure>
               <hi rend="latintype">per <lb/>
                  <term type="measure" ref="K01558">Ton</term>
               </hi> für <measure type="volume" quantity="800" unit="t" commodity="deadWeight">800</measure>
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <term type="measure" ref="K01558">Tons</term> Dead</hi>
            </p>
            <pb facs="1862_02_21_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Bourjau_Hubener_Co_Shanghai_2.tif" n="2"/>
            <pb facs="1862_02_21_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Bourjau_Hubener_Co_Shanghai_2.tif" n="3"/>
            <pb facs="1862_02_21_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Bourjau_Hubener_Co_Shanghai_1.tif" n="4"/>
            <p>
               <hi rend="latintype">weight</hi> worauf er <lb/>indeß nicht eingehen
                    <lb/>wollte:- Das Schiff <lb/>mit <measure type="volume" quantity="3000" unit="t">3000</measure>
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <term type="measure" ref="K01558">Tons</term> Mea- <lb/>surement Goods</hi>
                    zum <lb/>nämlichen Frachtwerte <lb/>aufzufüllen dazu <lb/>hatten wir keine
                    <lb/>Lust uns zu ver- <lb/>pflichten - Der gute <lb/>Mann dürfte sich <lb/>in
                    seinen <unclear reason="eccentric_ductus" cert="high">Hoffnun-</unclear>
               <lb/>gen etwas getäuscht <lb/> sehen + Ihren <unclear reason="eccentric_ductus">Markt</unclear>
               <lb/>bei Ankunft doch <lb/>nicht mehr so leb- <lb/>haft als kurze Zeit
                    <lb/>vorher finden + <lb/>somit gelingt es <lb/>Ihnen vielleicht doch <lb/>noch
                    mit ihm zu <lb/>Stande zu kommen <lb/>wir wollten nicht <lb/>unterlassen haben
                    <lb/>Ihnen obiges mitzu- <lb/>theilen. <term type="goods" ref="K01501">Kohlen</term> halten <lb/>sich auf <term type="currency" ref="K01525">Ts.</term>
               <measure type="currency" quantity="9" unit="tael" commodity="coal">9.</measure>
                    per <term type="measure" ref="K01558">Ton</term>
               <lb/>In Eile <lb/>
               <seg rend="center">Ihre</seg>
               <lb/>
               <seg rend="right">
                  <choice>
                     <abbr>pp</abbr>
                     <expan>per Procura</expan>
                  </choice>
                  <hi rend="latintype">
                     <orgName type="firm" ref="K01011">Bourjau Hübener <lb/>+C.</orgName>
                     <lb/>
                     <persName ref="K00071">Ernst Bèhre</persName>
                  </hi>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
   <text type="translation">
      <body>
         <pb facs="1862_02_21_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Bourjau_Hubener_Co_Shanghai_1.tif" n="1"/>
         <p>Shanghai the 21st Feb. 62<lb/>Messrs. L. Kniffler<lb/>&amp; C.<lb/>Nagasaki <lb/>
                Following on from our letter<lb/>we did not want to forego<lb/> the opportunity
                to<lb/> inform you that <del rend="overstrike">we</del>
            <lb/>a cargo offer<lb/> that we made the<lb/> captain of the <lb/>
            <unclear>Hound[?]</unclear> was not <lb/> accepted + that <lb/>she will sail to
                your<lb/> place within a few<lb/> days. Probably seeking<lb/> to speculate. We
                offered<lb/> him here$ 6. per <lb/> ton for 800 tons dead</p>
         <pb facs="1862_02_21_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Bourjau_Hubener_Co_Shanghai_2.tif" n="2"/>
         <pb facs="1862_02_21_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Bourjau_Hubener_Co_Shanghai_2.tif" n="3"/>
         <pb facs="1862_02_21_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Bourjau_Hubener_Co_Shanghai_1.tif" n="4"/>
         <p>weight, which he <lb/>was however not going to<lb/> accept: – To fill up<lb/> the
                ship with<lb/> 3,000 tons of mea- <lb/>surement goods up to <lb/>the named freight
                <lb/> values we did not have<lb/> the inclination of<lb/> obligating ourselves –
                The<lb/> good fellow may well see<lb/> his hopes[?] betrayed<lb/> somewhat + upon
                <lb/> his arrival not<lb/> find your market[?]<lb/> as lively any more<lb/>as it
                recently was + <lb/>thus you may still<lb/> succeed in getting<lb/> something
                agreed<lb/> with him. We did not <lb/> want to omit to<lb/> tell you the above.<lb/>
                Coals are remaining<lb/> at Ts. 9. per ton.<lb/> Hurriedly <lb/>your<lb/>pp Bourjau
                Hübener <lb/>+C. <lb/>Ernst Bèhre</p>
      </body>
